org.cyclops.cyclopscore.modcompat

Interface IExternalCompat

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IInitListener
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IApiCompat, IModCompat
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VersionCheckerModCompat

    public interface IExternalCompat
extends IInitListener
    Interface for external compatibilities. Implement this on classes that require external functionality that needs to be called in the preInit, init or postInit events. Add instances to the ModCompatLoader.compats list. Note that classes implementing this interface can NOT use classes from the targeted mod, since an instance of the Compat will be created anyways, and otherwise certain class definitions won't be found.
